            <div>
                <h3> Promo creation plan  </h3>
                <p>
                    <b class="add-number">1</b> <b>Define our target audience and the topic we will promote.</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b class="add-number">2</b> <b>Write a script for the future promo.</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b class="add-number">3</b> <b>Choose photo and video materials.</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b class="add-number">4</b> <b>Edit materials, add text blocks.</b>
                </p>
                <p>
                    <b class="add-number">5</b> <b>Add music and edit video (if it is a video).</b>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
