                <p>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" enable-background="new 0 0 105.68 29.15" version="1.1" viewBox="0 0 105.68 29.15" x="0px" xml:space="preserve" y="0px" style="fill: rgb(0, 0, 0); width: 30px"> <g id="__id292_s6xbsdnfsn"><path d="m77.67 24.68c1.24 3.73 4.31 5.3 7.96 4.05 5.08-1.73 10.13-3.56 15.1-5.57 5.95-2.42 6.7-7.49 1.33-10.91-6.56-4.18-13.45-7.88-20.37-11.44-4.01-2.07-6.73-0.03-6.8 4.6-0.02 1.58 0.04 3.16 0.07 5.16-1.65 0.03-2.96 0.04-4.26 0.07-20.97 0.38-41.94 0.75-62.91 1.17-1.6 0.03-3.24 0.16-4.77 0.58-2.29 0.64-3.25 2.18-2.97 4.14 0.27 1.89 1.77 3.13 4.06 3.13 1.74 0 3.48-0.3 5.23-0.35 21.37-0.6 42.74-1.19 64.11-1.75 0.9-0.02 1.8 0.19 2.73 0.29 0.51 2.41 0.78 4.69 1.49 6.83zm4.34-15.25c4.61 2.52 8.53 4.67 13.13 7.19-3.99 1.64-7.31 3-10.92 4.48-0.72-3.8-1.4-7.37-2.21-11.67z" style="fill: rgb(76, 111, 191);"></path></g> </svg>
