                <h3>Advertising with bloggers</h3>
                <div>
                    <p>
                        Creating demand for products and services with the help of
                        an opinion leader or group authority is one of <b class="text-warning">the most effective ways to promote</b>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        An <b class="text-warning">influencer</b> is considered to be someone who is able to influence
                        the decisions and opinions of others due to the presence of vast experience,
                        authority, or knowledge in a particular area.
                        If we talk about social networks, <b class="text-warning">bloggers are indisputably such people</b>.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        <b class="text-primary">*</b> but do not forget, that only bloggers with a similar target audience to yours will be suitable for advertising.
                        Similar, but not the same.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
