                        <b>Lead to ad</b> <br>
                         - Lead to ad is a one or few stories, where blogger prepares subscribers for advertising (tells about your brand) to
                        create trust in your product with the blogger's audience.
                        <br>
                         - Lead to ad may be in a survey format. <b class="text-warning">For example:</b> "Did you know that you can professionally edit video without having a powerful computer?
