                         - Lead to ad may be native. <b class="text-warning">For example:</b> blogger is going to an event and asks subscribers what to wear - and you gave a dress for advertising.
                        <br>
                         - Also, you will have to provide the theses-phrases about your blog (release on the phrases from the promo) that blogger should say in "lead to ad".
                    </p>
